"This is a vimrc file for the IdeaVIM plugin in Intellij"

"Mappings
"============================================================================
"jj goes from insertmode to normalmode
inoremap jj <ESC> 

"Mapping ctrl-c, ctrl-x and ctrl-v
vmap <C-c> "+yi
vmap <C-x> "+c
vmap <C-v> c<ESC>"+p
imap <C-v> <ESC>"+pa
"============================================================================
